{"tid":1948645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]不多於四人非同住群組拜山  廢老：無須理會","createTime":"2020-03-29T07:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T07:10:33.000Z","uid":73883,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7c07fb570caf3ea6269ab45e736ab2956634c3ae","tid":1948645,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuVBJ72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuVBJ72.png&h=25797ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzEyMmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzEyMmt.png&h=7c783c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re9bx1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre9bx1z.png&h=50821daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】公眾地方禁止多於四人聚集的新規例凌晨十二時起生效，市面人流冷清。不過臨近清明節，有人無視新例，多於四人一起掃墓；亦有外傭如常聚集及聚餐，場地保安員亦沒有阻止。 <br />\n<br />\n新例生效後第一個早上，銅鑼灣街頭人流冷清，看不到有多於四人聚集；但走遠一點去到中環，仍然看到這班熟客，三五成群的外傭坐在行人專用區的馬路上。<br />\n<br />\n皇后像廣場內依舊熱鬧，有些明顯是超過四人聚餐，保安員經過只是看兩眼，沒有勸他們散開。保安員在鏡頭下表示，他們只是負責捉小販。有外傭說知道新例生效，已經注意保持社交距離。有菲律賓民間組織在街上舉牌，提醒同鄉注意社交距離，保持個人衛生。<br />\n<br />\n新措施未有豁免掃墓，除非本身是同住，否則不可多於四人一起拜山。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在將軍澳墳場，大部分都是少於四人一起攜同祭品孝敬先人；但亦有群組多於四人。他們說雖然一家人不是同住，但沒有理由分開來祭祖。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n新例禁止多於四人在公眾地方聚集，有十二項情況獲豁免，包括共住的同一戶人。政府說授權人員，包括場地管理員和警察，如果發現有人違規，會作出驅散。政府呼籲市民盡量分散清明節前後拜山，以免出現人潮，增加病毒傳播風險。"},{"pid":"a9153e621ba30851706f0509caa945166c9efe39","tid":1948645,"uid":182195,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"無須理會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢唔戴口罩已經明哂"},{"pid":"028f4c008503ac4a516d17d987ca8d8e51b9b026","tid":1948645,"uid":7421,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"好快就有拜山家族<br />\n香港一日有呢d廢老一日都係無得救"},{"pid":"c2dbd03c50fdbe04cd87836a49b5a2e62c6622df","tid":1948645,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"係時候要做好市民報犬咬廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739986d17906d2d46f27b3146f12b3187a67c5bd","tid":1948645,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"等睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc49cd702317cbc5e73d6d0430e95e72f6e7013","tid":1948645,"uid":238920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"就算佢件例係on9,但點都要戴口罩掛??"},{"pid":"c4e44af7e0cd62e34a0bcd0060870e7e4eb5c765","tid":1948645,"uid":65289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"返支那拜山咪可以多過四個人一齊囉<br />\n唔送 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a507db47cd50c34cf37f8693f42566d47b0459","tid":1948645,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"藍絲： 無須理會 唔會拉我"},{"pid":"9ce7409d47848e6a82d896f8803debf6c8ede44e","tid":1948645,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"有冇片"},{"pid":"bbf7372c6a22a6628d5fa1c57a8ab9c4e3589c81","tid":1948645,"uid":31962,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"下年佢俾人拜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f373c0c8ff3d468f8eb82034cc26186e9ac679bd","tid":1948645,"uid":275688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e61e223eef16cb54c8f4323e9a9d346a50cfecb9","tid":1948645,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf7372c6a22a6628d5fa1c57a8ab9c4e3589c81","tid":1948645,"uid":31962,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"下年佢俾人拜山<img src=\"/assets/face